to access your Django on local network; do
	1- go to settings.py
		paste this 
			ALLOWED_HOSTS = ['127.0.0.1', 'localhost', 'YOUR_IP_ADDRESS']
		OR this
			ALLOWED_HOSTS = ['*']
		at the bottom (to override empty variable with same name)
	2- run python manage.py runserver YOUR_IP_ADDRESS:8000
	3- Now you can access this web from any local machine